ondsman Or Runner May Engage In Electronic Monitoring Of A Defendant; By Adding Section 38-53-84 To Provide That A Person Engaged In The Electronic Monitoring Of A Defendant Must Notify The Solicitor Within Forty-eight Hours Of Any Violation Of A Condition Of The Bond By The Defendant And To Provide That Failure To Pay The Monitoring Fees Is A Revokable Condition Of The Bond; By Amending Section 38-53-170, Relating To Unlawful Acts By A Bondsman, To Provide Conditions For The Payment And Collection Of Premiums, Fees, And Collateral; And By Amending Section 38-53-310, Relating To Written Report To Be Filed With Clerk Of Court, To Provide That A Bondsman Must Provide A Written Report To Their Insurance Provider Within Thirty Days Of Each Bond, And To Provide That The Requirement For Monthly Reports To The Clerk Of Court May Be Satisfied With Giving The Clerk Access To An Electronic Database That Contains The Required Information.","pending_committee_id":0,"committee":[],"referrals":[{"date":"2023-01-10","committee_id":727,"chamber":"S","chamber_id":86,"name":"Judiciary"}],"history":[{"date":"2023-01-10","action":"Introduced and read first time","chamber":"S","chamber_id":86,"importance":1},{"date":"2023-01-10","action":"Referred to Committee on Judiciary","chamber":"S","chamber_id":86,"importance":1},{"date":"2023-01-12","action":"Referred to Subcommittee: Malloy (ch), Sabb, Adams, Garrett, Gustafson","chamber":"S","chamber_id":86,"importance":1},{"date":"2023-02-09","action":"Scrivener's error corrected","chamber":"","chamber_id":0,"importance":0},{"date":"2023-02-22","action":"Committee report: Favorable with amendment Judiciary","chamber":"S","chamber_id":86,"importance":0}],"sponsors":[{"people_id":21778,"person_hash":"fg2ykbim","party_id":"2","state_id":40,"party":"R","role_id":2,"role":"Sen","name":"Brian Adams","first_name":"Brian","middle_name":"R.","last_name":"Adams","suffix":"","nickname":"","district":"SD-044","ftm_eid":23356113,"votesmart_id":191565,"open